        "text": "We, from the Data Driven Marketing Association (DDMA), support and align with the position expressed by FEDMA in its consultation response. In particular, we emphasize the importance of coherence with the existing EU legal framework and the need to prioritise effective enforcement and guidance over the creation of new legislative layers. Our members (large and small companies that focus on data-driven marketing) also struggle to keep up with the growing complexity of overlapping rules. We therefore prefer clearer interpretation and coordination of existing legislation rather than the addition of new rules.",
