          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 12426,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "The influencer marketing landscape is governed by many different laws and codes. In the Netherlands it is covered by the Mediawet and the Advertising Code for Social Media and Influencer Marketing. Harmonisation of rules and definitions at EU level could therefore be beneficial, but introducing additional obligations would only create more confusion and force stakeholders to search across multiple sources to understand their responsibilities. The current framework is already complex for the sector (influencers and agencies) to navigate and comply with.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s5",
          "section_path": [
            "Dark patterns:",
            "Influencer Marketing:"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 81,
          "char_len": 558
